Nulakazi was the language spoken by the pre-[[Sundering]] [[Sarlona]]n Empire of [[Nulakaz]], at various points in history was spoken across [[Dor Maleer]], [[Rhiavhaar]], [[Caleshaz]], [[Borunan]], and [[Pyrine]], as well as parts of the southern [[Tashana Tundra]]. Nulakazi is a linguistic ancestor of the [[Common]] tongue of [[Khorvaire]], and it also strongly influenced the modern [[Riedran]] language.